{"tid":1741213,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"暴聯會號召一批市民到紅隧清理垃圾 遭警方拒絕進入封鎖線範圍","createTime":"2019-11-20T08:42:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-20T08:42:52.000Z","uid":212626,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7942a9ec3ef8adb6b84ed17615d6a55c982d8e54","tid":1741213,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T08:42:52.000Z","msg":"一批市民下午原先打算在紅隧九龍入口附近清理路障，遭警方拒絕他們進入封鎖線範圍，他們改為到香港體育館平台及附近清理垃圾。<br />\n<br />\n帶隊的工聯會會長吳秋北說，希望號召全港市民一起清潔香港，團結一致止暴制亂，對抗「黑色暴力」，呼籲群眾離開時沿途清理垃圾，協助盡快恢復香港原貌。<br />\n<br />\n對於立法會前主席曾鈺成，日前進入理大校園與示威者對話，吳秋北認為，觸犯法例的人應該主動自首。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1493478-20191120.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1493478-20191120.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=Cf%2BepIHKvYs8nB0OclbNLJR%2B4kUINcy65scadR%2F1ewI%3D&h=e75df743\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1493478-20191120.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=dca3cea2\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1493478-20191120.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"}]}